import base64
import datetime
import glob
import hashlib
import json
import multiprocessing
import os
import random
import string


nonce = ''.join(random.sample(string.ascii_uppercase + string.ascii_lowercase + string.digits, k=8)).encode('utf-8')
timestamp = datetime.datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%dT%TZ').encode('utf-8')
password = '2jzSh'.encode('utf-8')

b64_nonce = base64.b64encode(nonce)
b64_sha_pass = base64.b64encode(hashlib.sha1(nonce + timestamp + hashlib.sha1(password).digest()).digest())


nonce=b64_nonce.decode('utf-8')
password=b64_sha_pass.decode('utf-8')
timestamp=timestamp.decode('utf-8')
